cat << EOF
Gv4l is a GUI frontend for the V4L (Video For Linux) functions of transcode,
used to record video (and audio) streams from a V4L devices, such as tuners and
webcams, in encoded (Xvid, DivX, etc.) or raw video formats.  If you try Gv4l,
give me some feedback. Developers, code, patches, ideas, money, etc. are
welcome. Feel free to drop an e-mail (warder@warder.ath.cx) or post a message
at the Forum.
EOF
